m:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQ1iMVHbJrZWX8IA5y64pXQU1h87eU2NLf-2-RRfMRTX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09HMCQF4S%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09HMCQF4S/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=A2O1709E31Q2KL&amp;psc=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">JLab Go Air Pop</a> 。目前它的售价为 16 美元，比历史最低价高出几美元，但比近几个月的正常市场价格低 7 美元。我们在预算无线耳机指南中重点介绍了 Go Air Pop：它的价格比 Jackson 还低，它提供了紧凑的设计、八小时左右的电池续航时间、IPX4 防水性能和全套功能性触摸控制。虽然没有应用程序，但 JLab 将三个 EQ 预设烘焙到耳塞本身中。轰鸣的声音比 EarFun Free 2S 差，但这是一套售价 16 美元的耳塞，还算不错。作为主对的备用，你可能会做得更糟。</p><h2> Beats Studio 耳机 + </h2><p><core-commerce id="3c6c1b9457704f1587079d7df727389e" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Prime Day 为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:40;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJaSzJaMlRDP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvay0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYTExZDkzY2EtNzdhMi00OGVjLTgyOGUtMGZkNmY4MDUzNTMwIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAbh5oq78MFoY3hRmvARvG0Zwgb5LUBfI54XHFEyAPqcp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BZK2Z2TC" class="rapid-with-clickid">Beats Studio Buds +</a>带来了首次折扣，最近发布的这双耳机可享受 20 美元的折扣，原价 150 美元。我们在 5 月份给这些耳塞<a data-i13n="cpos:41;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/beats-studio-buds-plus-review-140028329.html">评分为 84 分</a>，称赞其与原版 Studio Buds 相比改进的声音、ANC 和通话质量。就像那对一样，它们小巧而舒适，但它们不使用 Apple H1 或 H2 芯片，因此它们缺乏某些 AirPods 风格的功能，例如自动设备切换和音频共享。不过，快速配对、查找我的跟踪和免提 Siri 等其他功能仍然可用，Beats 在 Android 上也支持类似功能。需要明确的是，Studio Buds + 的 ANC、电池续航时间和音质表现落后于 <a data-i13n="cpos:42;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">我们购买指南</a>中的首选，而且它们缺乏自动暂停和无线充电功能，这令人难以接受。但如果你想要一套价格低于 AirPods Pro 的苹果耳机，它们应该很有吸引力。</p><p>如需更便宜的替代品， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:43;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDk2U1NDVjVLP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvay0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYTExZDkzY2EtNzdhMi00OGVjLTgyOGUtMGZkNmY4MDUzNTMwIn0&amp;signature=AQAAARfIlbRy6uDgy8-WzH40k8ZGmrplrPaFwIoM4OvrPtd3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB096SSCV5K" class="rapid-with-clickid">基本版 Studio Buds 的</a>售价为 90 美元。它们并不比 Space A40 更好，但如果您喜欢 Studio Buds 的美感，它们<a data-i13n="cpos:44;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/beats-studio-buds-review-150014566.html">仍然不错</a>。</p><h2>节拍 Powerbeats Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="4de361b0ec144ec9aed6d9bcc23952d0" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Prime 会员的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:45;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdSNVFENTk4P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvay0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYTExZDkzY2EtNzdhMi00OGVjLTgyOGUtMGZkNmY4MDUzNTMwIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAYPjufnEi90_hg9vHc9N6V-2HKeN9Gn1I8r-RvQwgxmu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07R5QD598" class="rapid-with-clickid">Beats Powerbeats Pro</a>价格降至 150 美元，大约有 40 美元的折扣，与我们追踪到的最低价格相符。该款耳机采用耳挂设计，可在锻炼期间保持稳定，并且物理控制按钮可在您移动时轻松使用。它的电池续航时间长达 10 小时左右，而且声音相当精准，没有 Beats 过去那种臃肿的低音。它还使用苹果的 H1 芯片，可以在 iOS 上实现一些 AirPods 式的便利。然而，它的充电盒很大，而且它并没有完全密封耳朵，所以它不会阻挡太多的外部噪音。当 Powerbeats Pro 于 2019 年推出时，我们给了<a data-i13n="cpos:46;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-05-16-beats-powerbeats-pro-review.html">它 86 分</a>。</p><p>我们还会提到<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQNwSJ7VyFFzaxTs2mZm3bRYxZapvEt4MehiGZBfuOHP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Fit-Pro-Cancelling-Built%2Fdp%2FB09JL41N9C" class="rapid-with-clickid">Beats Fit Pro</a> ；这一款在 Prime Day 期间并没有大幅折扣，但它是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html#bestforworkoutsbeatsfitpro">在整体锻炼中最喜欢的真无线耳机</a>，而且它采用了更传统的入耳式设计。</p><h2>索尼 LinkBuds S </h2><p><core-commerce id="85e652658fbf4ede9feb10573c13d3b0" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaEKQ4Hy64-SUTqyxVAEjKx9hBCdxdvJ8WVxiSlo8BfU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09YL296PM%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09YL296PM/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Sony LinkBuds S</a>的售价为 128 美元，创下历史最低价，比市场平均价格低约 35 美元。这是我们的无线耳塞指南中的荣誉奖，因为它采用了易于佩戴的小型设计，具有不错的 ANC 功能和价格合理的音质，并且与其他索尼耳机一样，还有一套有用​​的附加功能。</p><p>我们指南中的首选是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDk0QzRWREpaP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvay0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYTExZDkzY2EtNzdhMi00OGVjLTgyOGUtMGZkNmY4MDUzNTMwIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAQ1BBlw9crkvETWvkZARJ51RyopEM7Edug_vKFFdl44u&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB094C4VDJZ" class="rapid-with-clickid">索尼的 WF-1000XM4</a> ，价格降至 198 美元，但我们不太愿意称其为划算的价格。耳塞本身 <a data-i13n="cpos:51;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-wf-1000xm4-review-160006474.html">很棒</a>，比 LinkBuds S（尽管框架更大）具有更好的电池寿命、音质和 ANC。但<a data-i13n="cpos:53;pos:1" href="https://thewalkmanblog.blogspot.com/2023/06/sony-wf-1000xm5-leaked-announcement-soon.html">最近的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:52;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-wf-1000xm5-leak-offers-a-first-look-at-the-unannounced-earbuds-161044694.html">几份</a><a data-i13n="cpos:54;pos:1" href="https://www.androidpolice.com/sony-upcoming-flagship-earbuds-could-offer-big-leap-sound-quality/">报道</a>表明索尼将在不久的将来推出后续产品。大多数人现在应该暂缓购买当前的型号，特别是因为我们在过去几个月的大部分时间里都看到了这个交易价格。</p><h2>谷歌 Pixel Buds Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="268dba4da06a400cafa7eb02ce176045" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:55;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEIxTjdaOEIzP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvay0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiYTExZDkzY2EtNzdhMi00OGVjLTgyOGUtMGZkNmY4MDUzNTMwIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAclSzIh3Vf3rIxRlaqB83mDoOAAKcMIMOXqciLYKesUx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0B1N7Z8B3" class="rapid-with-clickid">Google Pixel Buds Pro</a>售价降至 139 美元，与该耳塞的历史最低价相差不到 5 美元，比一般价格低约 45 美元。这是我们购买指南中“最适合 Android 的选择”，因为它提供了 AirPods 式的与谷歌操作系统和 Pixel 手机的集成。它的 ANC 和有力<a data-i13n="cpos:56;pos:1" href="https://www.headphonesty.com/2017/01/v-shaped-sound-signature-mean/">的 V 形</a>声音轮廓令人愉悦（尽管不是最高级），并且在关闭 ANC 的情况下可以获得 11 个小时左右的电池续航时间（或者在开启 ANC 的情况下获得不错的 7 小时）。然而，它的通话质量和透明模式表现平平，对于耳朵较小的人来说，佩戴起来可能会很困难。尽管如此，当折扣达到这种程度时，这是一个不错的中档选择。去年我们给 Pixel Buds Pro 的<a data-i13n="cpos:57;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-buds-review-170044941.html">评分为 87 分</a>。</p><h2>森海塞尔 HD 560S </h2><p><core-commerce id="3bc09b628ace492aa7d599ba0ff6612d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>经典的有线耳机不像以前那么方便，但对于在家中进行关键的聆听或游戏来说， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWU5HtZFqDqTXcVzGvdh-G4njoVK-3_9tH41XgzOCVil&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSennheiser-HD-Over-Audiophile-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB08J9MVB6W%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Sennheiser HD 560S 的</a>价格非常实惠，售价为 142 美元。这比这双鞋的典型市场价格低约 25 美元。我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-headset-130006477.html">最佳游戏耳机</a>指南中推荐 HD 560S：它没有麦克风，但其平衡的声音轮廓和宽广的声场使游戏听起来更加身临其境和细致。它也可以很好地转化为音乐，即使它的高音可能有点热。舒适度不是问题，但由于这是一款开放式耳机，因此会泄漏并引入大量噪音。</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:61;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:62;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>亚