>对即将离任的首席运营官谢丽尔·桑德伯格 (Sheryl Sandberg) 进行了调查</a>，指控她利用公司资源来实现个人目标，例如婚礼策划或试图压制批评她前合伙人鲍比·科蒂克 (Bobby Kotick) 的新闻报道。然而，马斯克作为主要首席执行官的形象使这个案例脱颖而出。</p><p>这位领导人对法律纠纷并不陌生。他仍然卷入<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-loses-appeal-to-tweet-whatever-he-wants-about-tesla-190942572.html">与美国证券交易委员会因推特财务数据而发生的争执</a>，并在英国洞穴探险家弗农·昂斯沃斯因未经证实的“恋童癖”指控而提起的诽谤诉讼中幸存下来。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/tesla-reportedly-suspected-musk-was-using-company-funds-to-build-a-literal-glass-house-193314854.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tesla-reportedly-suspected-musk-was-using-company-funds-to-build-a-literal-glass-house-193314854.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3a4ca2dc-7489-4202-b7e8-1216f0852d06</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 19:33:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689104248</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T19:37:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="2427" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/b355b570-f4b5-11ed-afaf-ba29cffb01b4" width="3641"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2427" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/b355b570-f4b5-11ed-afaf-ba29cffb01b4" width="3641"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA