take advantage of some of the offers, but thankfully, not every discount is Prime-exclusive this year.如果您一直想购买新平板电脑，以下是我们可以找到的亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳平板电脑优惠。</p><h2>苹果 iPad（第 9 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="a217428324574d4da9b0f30ea9176424" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlHOUZQSFk2P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAR4RanmH0u4y6mVZaDJZzkYomqpnAtu8p-cYM8jFx-3k&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G9FPHY6" class="rapid-with-clickid">10.2 英寸 iPad</a>售价降至 250 美元，与该平板电脑的历史最低价持平。苹果通常以 329 美元的价格出售这款 64GB 型号，但过去几个月的大部分时间我们经常看到它的零售价在 275 美元左右。第 9 代 iPad 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">iPad 购买指南</a>中的首选预算选择，2021 年我们给它的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-9th-generation-review-143045685.html">评分为 86 分</a>。如果您需要更多存储空间， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlHOTFUTE5KP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAActU3VFjJSpfnstly-W3h4jUWlZBPHQ3Qqxq52jvmHsS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G91TLNJ" class="rapid-with-clickid">256GB 型号</a>也以 389 美元的价格出售。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这款 iPad 的设计与较新型号相比已经过时，因为它仍然具有 Lightning 端口、Home 按钮、厚边框和非层压显示屏。但它仍然为你提供了大量的应用程序，而且它的 A13 Bionic 芯片仍然足够快，适合轻松工作和休闲媒体消费。它也是目前唯一一款仍然带有耳机插孔的 iPad。</p><h2>苹果iPad Air </h2><p><core-commerce id="b667a774c2564a5282c713e840de5c21" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWM0hOMUtDP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZmEyYmU4NTEtNmIzMy00NDQ1LWEyNjgtMDc1ZGM4ZWM2MjU2In0&amp;signature=AQAAAQrRp1X1r3sGnv6Z10V1r94Iq4tjpAgd866GBST83p1h&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09V3HN1KC" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09V3HN1KC?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">iPad Air</a>是我们向大多数人推荐的 iPad，目前售价 500 美元。这是我们过去几个月大部分时间看到的价格，但它是 100 美元<strong>&nbsp;</strong>低于苹果的建议零售价。 The Air 去年获得了<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-air-5th-generation-review-130019050.html">90 分的评价</a>。虽然它缺乏 iPad Pro 的 120Hz 刷新率、128GB 基本存储和更好的扬声器，但它以更少的成本提供了同样优雅的设计，与第 9 代和第 10 代相比，它具有更快的 M1 芯片、卓越的显示屏和更广泛的配件支持。一代 iPad。</p><h2>苹果 iPad（第 10 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="c5f3a225cb9d4f43964277c5b8a80c0d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> 64GB <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtV