amp;signature=AQAAAXs8pz_zrTjtUS8AaVc9z9CYvWhySKp4o6Th1MQHMEPO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G9FPHY6" class="rapid-with-clickid">苹果第 9 代 iPad</a>降价至 250 美元，这是迄今为止最优惠的价格，因为它的正常售价为 329 美元。这是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">最佳 iPad 指南</a>中的预算之选。虽然它没有我们最喜欢的 iPad Air 那样的窄边框和那么多配件支持，但它是购买 iPad 最实惠的方式。它是一款出色的沙发伴侣，非常适合休闲浏览、观看流媒体和轻度游戏。</p><p>最新一代（第 10 代） <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJKTENXRk5NP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZvr2_DwsO2dym1v3QvU_coqE-0-zZNySmqSJ1btc_Un&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BJLCWFNM" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BJLCWFNM?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple 64GB 标准版 iPad</a>折扣 70 美元后，现价降至 380 美元。它有一个稍大的屏幕和更新的芯片（尽管不是苹果自己的 M 系列芯片）。最新一代还放弃了主页按钮，这很好，但取消了耳机插孔，这不太好。</p><h2> MacBook Air M1 </h2><p><core-commerce id="234f60531f574d228c10e486d83bf01b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> If you want a steep bargain on an Apple laptop, go for 2020&#39;s <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARoBT_99zjj_Wcz5lmIA7pDrBDIN9-uqbtRzEQ8iokp9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MacBook-13-inch-256GB-Storage%2Fdp%2FB08N5LNQCX" class="rapid-with-clickid">MacBook Air with the M1 chip</a> . It&#39;s still a capable laptop and the 256GB base model is just $750 for Prime Day, which is the lowest price we&#39;ve seen so far on the ultraportable. It&#39;s the budget pick in our <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-macbook-140032524.html">buyer&#39;s guide to Macbooks</a> and earned a <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-macbook-air-m1-review-140031323.html">high score of 94</a> in our review.</p><p> The performance of the M1 chip really makes the MacBook Air M1 stand out. It&#39;s responsive, launching apps quickly and running them effortlessly. The M1 chip is also behind the MB Air&#39;s great battery life. We clocked 16 hours and 20 minutes of play time in our video rundown test, which should be more than enough to get you through a full day of work or study.</p><h2>小型平板电脑</h2><p><core-commerce id="9deb0115288047edac25b52a7800b2ad" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>像<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlHOTFMWEZQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE5OC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNTZkOWY4OWQtNWFmOS00MjdhLWIxNWYtMWU5OTdjNWFiMDBmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAdmjsmdQm75aE4mQZ8cNXuA-vNzZuxWpyX1iB4rkt8Gy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09G91LXFP" class="rapid-with-clickid">iPad mini</a>这样的小型平板电脑可以完成手机的许多功能，同时为您提供更多的屏幕空间。 For Prime Day, Apple&#39;s diminutive slate is $380 for Prime members instead of its usual $499.由于其新颖的设计和稳定的性能，我们在<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-mini-6th-generation-2021-review-130009170.html">评测</a>中给了 mini 89 分。它还与第二代<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXytOIsQTlSMWEu0r7dlhAGSrfNYne9qXWOs9Ks1tgAm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Pencil</a>完美搭配，将 mini 变成便携式数字笔记本。</p><p> The iPad mini comes with a 12MP ultra wide front camera that supports Center Stage, a feature that pans and zooms to keep you in frame during video calls. As for battery life, Apple estimates going for 10 hours on a charge, but we got two hours longer than that on our video run down test, and only had to charge it every other day with casual but regular use.</p><h2> Apple Pencil（第二代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="a7ac3b8968534a1c92a72870c4a3db68" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>最新款<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXytOIsQTlSMWEu0r7dlhAGSrfNYne9qXWOs9Ks1tgAm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation%2Fdp%2FB07K1WWBJK" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple Pencil</a>通常售价 129 美元，但 Prime Day 仅需 89 美元。第二代手写笔<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLXVzL0hUMjExMDI5IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI1NmQ5Zjg5ZC01YWY5LTQyN2EtYjE1Zi0xZTk5N2M1YWIwMGYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXtu_NE0TTlHg9RLDBVrc0d_HMnVhP2lk8kdVtiXQc_U&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT211029" class="rapi