d">SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7X 的</a>售价为 150 美元，这是我们见过的最低价格，比通常的市场价格低了约 25 美元。我们在游戏耳机指南中指出 Arctis Nova 7X 对于 Xbox 用户来说是一个值得选择的无线选择。它的麦克风质量很稳定，尽管比价格更高的 Nova Pro 差一些，而且随着时间的推移佩戴起来很舒适，布质耳垫不会压得太紧。它具有低音前移的声音轮廓，因此爆炸和其他效果具有真正的魅力，尽管高音的下降可能会使游戏中的对话声音被低估。不过，除了无线适配器之外，这款产品还可以通过蓝牙或 3.5 毫米电缆进行连接，而且一次充电可持续使用 30 多个小时。</p><h2>雷蛇猎魂迷你版</h2><p><core-commerce id="b31ef83b0e9e4c1bacdb85ba355b057a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>紧凑型<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAd2S9ZVEGupLeKU_fxLjP70G3RJDlpZC8MvCrnx69kIN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRazer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB08BFF4C7J%2F" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Razer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard/dp/B08BFF4C7J/?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Razer Huntsman Mini</a>配备<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:48;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAd2S9ZVEGupLeKU_fxLjP70G3RJDlpZC8MvCrnx69kIN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRazer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB08BFF4C7J%2F" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Razer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard/dp/B08BFF4C7J/?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Clicky Purple</a>或<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:49;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAad8cEs_Qtp8RGEvugGOQp_PgNNcB5u156ZEoEfyoKDV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRazer-Huntsman-Mini-Gaming-Keyboard%2Fdp%2FB08B3JSKGR" cl